  "keywords": [],
  "notes": [],
  "overnight": false,
  "slug": "spanish-peasant-potatoes",
  "source": "This recipe is based on [Spanish poor man’s potatoes recipe](https://spainonafork.com/spanish-poor-mans-potatoes-one-of-spains-most-iconic-dishes/) by Spain on a Fork.",
  "steps": [
    {
      "name": "",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "Cut the potatoes into large chunks, and cook them either in salted water, until they softened a bit for about 15 minutes, or in an air fryer at 210C for 18 minutes with olive oil and salt. (The potatoes should be 99% ready, and not very soft.)",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Wile the potatoes are cooking, take a Dutch oven (or a very large skillet), and start warming the bacon on medium heat.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Prepare the vegetables. Chili: remove the roots and seeds, and thinly slice. Onion: peel, halve, and slice into 1/2 cm slices. Garlic: crush and peel.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "When the bacon gets crispy, add the onions, chili, and garlic, add olive oil if the bacon didn’t release enough fat, and cook until the onion is transparent.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "When the potatoes are ready, discard the water, and let them dry for a bit.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "While the bacon with vegetables are cooking, remove the roots and seeds of bell peppers, and cut them into thin strips.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the coriander seeds, and fennel seeds to the vegetables and bacon, stir, and cook for another minute.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the bell peppers to the vegetables and bacon, and cook until the peppers soften.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the potatoes, and cook, stirring occasionally, until the potatoes are fully cooked.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add more salt if needed.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Serve sprinkled with chopped parsley.",
          "pause": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
